{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"154se","text":"Design Pattern Decisions","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"56hlq","text":"Circuit Breaker","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7smfl","text":"I implemented this with a boolean that checks if the contract is \"stopped.\" Only the admin should have this.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4gpe7","text":"This allows the contract to stop if a bug has been detected and provides time for developers to fix the bug.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"atn3b","text":"Fail early and fail loud","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1k00v","text":"I implemented this in multiple functions through the use of modifiers. For example, I  check if the user is the source of a resource with \"isSource\", and as another example I check if the emergency stop is active before the contract executes functions like \"notify()\".","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2e6gu","text":"I did this because debugging is easier and the end user will be notified of failure quickly.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"68rrs","text":"Restricting Access","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8t5b0","text":"Some functions, like the one that activates the circuit breaker, requires the admin account","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2ssdh","text":"I did this because some functions should not be accessible by everyone.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}